    "html": "<h2> O Partic铆pio Qal</h2><p>O <strong>partic铆pio</strong> 茅 uma forma verbal que funciona como adjetivo ou substantivo, expressando a莽茫o cont铆nua ou estado.</p><h3> Formas do Partic铆pio</h3><table style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;'><tr style='background: var(--color-primary); color: white;'><th style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>G锚nero/N煤mero</th><th style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Ativo</th><th style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Passivo</th></tr><tr><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Masc. Sing.</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>止旨转值</span> (kotev - escrevendo)</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>指旨转旨</span> (katuv - escrito)</td></tr><tr><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Fem. Sing.</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>止旨转侄侄转</span> (kotevet)</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>职旨转旨指</span> (ketuvah)</td></tr><tr><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Masc. Plur.</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>止旨转职执</span> (kotvim)</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>职旨转旨执</span> (ketuvim)</td></tr><tr><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'>Fem. Plur.</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>止旨转职止转</span> (kotvot)</td><td style='padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;'><span class='hebrew'>职旨转旨止转</span> (ketuvot)</td></tr></table><h2> O Verbo 指指 (ser/estar)</h2><p>O verbo <span class='hebrew'>指指</span> 茅 irregular e fundamental:</p><h3>Qal Perfeito:</h3><ul style='margin-left: 2rem;'><li><span class='hebrew'>指指</span> (hayah - ele foi/era)</li><li><span class='hebrew'>指职转指</span> (haytah - ela foi/era)</li><li><span class='hebrew'>指执转执</span> (hayiti - eu fui/era)</li></ul><h3>Qal Imperfeito:</h3><ul style='margin-left: 2rem;'><li><span class='hebrew'>执职侄</span> (yihyeh - ele ser谩)</li><li><span class='hebrew'>转执旨职侄</span> (tihyeh - ela ser谩)</li><li><span class='hebrew'>侄职侄</span> (ehyeh - eu serei)</li></ul>"
